{"tid":1104035,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實政府係高過13個月糧， 計 MPF","createTime":"2019-04-12T22:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T11:03:59.000Z","uid":90323,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dee54b6573ddeab9691b3c2865686dec3a4dfaac","tid":1104035,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T22:08:12.000Z","msg":"其實條數好淺， 不過你地隨便睇一眼喇。<br />\n<br />\n做夠3年， 佢MPF供 15%,<br />\n<br />\n咁多10% * 12,<br />\n咪多左1.2 個月囉。<br />\n<br />\n仲要愈供愈多， 去到25%,<br />\n<br />\n最後多左0.2*12, 其實咪14個月糧囉。<br />\n<br />\n而家個個point 16 退休攞住200個去玩。<br />\n<br />\n點醒私人巿場嘅普通人喇。<br />\n而家就算唔跳point,  政府而家個奇怪升幅一路超前緊私人巿場。<br />\n<br />\nCA唔駛做嘅文員2 萬， ACO通常都係唔駛做(有可能好忙)  嘅文員3.3 萬， 出面文員做到死有萬8 都好好。  老細會同你講， 密當勞經理都係萬幾。<br />\n<br />\n講做工程， 人工3萬以上大部份都要加班。<br />\n咁當然， 呢d專科都有追到私人巿場嘅例子。<br />\n不過一個 technical officer位已經令到好多人放棄駁專業考牌果條路。"},{"pid":"5ffc1e45c024a04460eebe731dcaf0a101fabfcc","tid":1104035,"uid":51250,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T22:11:13.000Z","msg":"你條數冇計錯<br />\n但退休先有得拎返點同double pay每年有得出比較 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac414431c359369fafb87331157309d51d9c4b15","tid":1104035,"uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5ffc1e45c024a04460eebe731dcaf0a101fabfcc","tid":1104035,"uid":51250,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T22:11:13.000Z","msg":"你條數冇計錯<br />\n但退休先有得拎返點同double pay每年有得出比較 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T23:33:03.000Z","msg":"但佢高過13個月好多麻。<br />\n<br />\n咁又唔係急錢駛"},{"pid":"71a2eda335c4f1bff1d811bf7c7324a735157533","tid":1104035,"uid":118212,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ac414431c359369fafb87331157309d51d9c4b15","tid":1104035,"uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5ffc1e45c024a04460eebe731dcaf0a101fabfcc","tid":1104035,"uid":51250,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T2